$ID,2$$FG,5$To convert old pictures...
$FG$1) Boot the old LoseThos version
2) Press CTRL-R when on top of the picture
3) Select "Insert"
4) Select "Convert to Bitmap".  If you don't want it drawn on a background, select "transparent bitmap."
5) Stretch-out a box around the image
6) Click "End"
7) Click "End" again
8) Save your picture in a file
9) Boot the new version of LoseThos

$FG,5$Another option you might try$FG$ 
1) Press CTRL-R
2) Select "Edit"
3) find the "Width" entries and change the far right numbers.
4) Press ESC
5) Select "End"
6) Save your picture in a file
